### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Create Job - Add Numbers (with async processing)
# Returns: 201 Created with { jobId: string, status: string }
# Request body: { num1: number, num2: number }
POST http://localhost:3000/add-numbers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "num1": 10,
    "num2": 20
}

###

### Check Job Status by ID
# Replace <jobId> with actual job ID from add-numbers response
# Returns: 200 OK with { jobId: string, status: string }
# Returns: 404 Not Found with { message: "Job not found" }
GET http://localhost:3000/check-numbers-state/<jobId>

###

### Get Job Result by ID
# Replace <jobId> with actual job ID from add-numbers response
# Returns: 200 OK with { jobId: string, status: string, input: { num1: number, num2: number }, result: { sum: number } } when completed
# Returns: 202 Accepted with { message: "Job not completed yet" } when still processing
# Returns: 404 Not Found with { message: "Job not found" } when job doesn't exist
GET http://localhost:3000/get-numbers-sum-by-job-id/<jobId>

###

### Example: Complete Flow
# Step 1: Create a job
POST http://localhost:3000/add-numbers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "num1": 5,
    "num2": 8
}

###

# Step 2: Check status (copy jobId from Step 1 response)
# GET http://localhost:3000/check-numbers-state/01963b2d-4c8e-7890-b123-456789abcdef

###

# Step 3: Get result (after ~5 seconds, copy jobId from Step 1 response)
# GET http://localhost:3000/get-numbers-sum-by-job-id/01963b2d-4c8e-7890-b123-456789abcdef

###

### Example with Invalid Input (Validation Error)
# Returns: 400 Bad Request with { message: "Validation error" }
POST http://localhost:3000/add-numbers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "num1": "not a number",
    "num2": true
}

###
